│</span>               <span class="topo-muted">▼</span>                                                      <span class="topo-muted">│
│</span>  <span class="topo-accent">┌──────────────────────────┐</span>  <span class="topo-accent">┌───────────────────┐</span>   <span class="topo-muted">│
