│</span>  <span class="topo-accent">│</span>  ├─ immich:2283    <span class="topo-live">[●]</span>  <span class="topo-accent">│</span>  <span class="topo-accent">│</span>  └─ ml:3003 <span class="topo-live">[●]</span><span class="topo-accent">│</span>   <span class="topo-muted">│
