      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 3: Hardware Nodes (neofetch style)
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="lab-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-intro homelab-animate">
      <h2 class="section-heading">The hardware</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        The primary server is a repurposed Intel MacBook running Ubuntu headless - lid closed, display off, always on.
        A custom systemd service handles the lid-close without suspending. The second node is a Windows laptop with an
        NVIDIA GPU that handles computationally expensive machine learning tasks over the local network.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="section-cmd">
      <span class="prompt-dollar">$</span> ssh prince@ubuntu-mac && ssh prince@windows-gpu
    </div>
    <div class="hardware-grid">
      <!-- MacBook Node -->
      <div class="terminal homelab-animate">
        <div class="terminal__bar">
          <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--red"></span>
          <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--yellow"></span>
          <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--green"></span>
          <span class="terminal__bar-title">ssh: ubuntu-mac</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal__content">
          <div class="neofetch">
            <div class="neofetch__hostname"><span class="prompt-user">prince</span>@<span class="prompt-user">ubuntu-mac</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__sep">─────────────────────</div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">OS</span><span class="neofetch__value">Ubuntu Server 22.04</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Host</span><span class="neofetch__value">Intel MacBook (Headless)</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Role</span><span class="neofetch__value">Primary Server</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">IP</span><span class="neofetch__value">192.168.0.104</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Uptime</span><span class="neofetch__value">24/7 (sleep disabled)</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">WiFi</span><span class="neofetch__value">Broadcom BCM4360</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Storage</span><span class="neofetch__value">Samsung T7 Shield SSD</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Docker</span><span class="neofetch__value">Compose V2 (plugin)</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Special</span><span class="neofetch__value">Custom lid-monitor daemon</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Windows GPU Node -->
      <div class="terminal homelab-animate">
        <div class="terminal__bar">
          <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--red"></span>
          <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--yellow"></span>
          <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--green"></span>
          <span class="terminal__bar-title">ssh: windows-gpu</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal__content">
          <div class="neofetch">
            <div class="neofetch__hostname"><span class="prompt-user">prince</span>@<span class="prompt-user">windows-gpu</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__sep">─────────────────────</div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">OS</span><span class="neofetch__value">Windows + WSL2</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Host</span><span class="neofetch__value">NVIDIA GPU Laptop</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Role</span><span class="neofetch__value">ML Offload Node</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">IP</span><span class="neofetch__value">192.168.0.197</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">GPU</span><span class="neofetch__value">NVIDIA CUDA (v545+)</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Service</span><span class="neofetch__value">Immich ML (face/object)</span></div>
            <div class="neofetch__row"><span class="neofetch__label">Port</span><span class="neofetch__value">3003</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 4: Services (systemctl style)
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="lab-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-intro homelab-animate">
      <h2 class="section-heading">What's running</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Nine services run across the two nodes, split into three categories.
        Every externally-accessible service goes through Cloudflare Tunnels - no ports are opened on the router.
        Each card below shows the service name, its status, and the engineering decisions behind it.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="section-cmd">
      <span class="prompt-dollar">$</span> systemctl list-units --type=service --state=running
    </div>

    <!-- Core Infrastructure -->
    <div class="service-group">
      <div class="service-group__label"><span class="comment-hash">#</span> ─── Core Infrastructure ───────────────────────────</div>

      <div class="service-card homelab-animate">
        <div class="service-card__status-bar"></div>
        <div class="service-card__content">
          <div class="service-card__header">
            <span class="service-card__dot service-card__dot--live"></span>
            <img class="service-card__icon-img" src="/icons/cloudflare.svg" alt="" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="service-card__name">cloudflared.service</span>
            <span class="service-card__title">- Secure Reverse Tunnel</span>
            <span class="live-pill"><span class="live-pill__dot"></span>LIVE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__meta">
            <span class="service-card__active">Active: active (running)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__details">
            <div class="service-card__row">
              <span class="service-card__key">Exposes</span>
              <span class="service-card__val">
                <a href="https://immich.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">immich.princejain.me</a>,
                <a href="https://vault.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vault.princejain.me</a>,
                <a href="https://pdf.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pdf.princejain.me</a>,
                <a href="https://n8n.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">n8n.princejain.me</a>,
                <a href="https://portainer.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">portainer.princejain.me</a>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card__row">
              <span class="service-card__key">Mode</span>
              <span class="service-card__val">systemd (host-level, not Docker)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__decisions">
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> Outbound-only tunnel - zero open ports on the router</div>
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> Free TLS, DDoS protection, and WAF from Cloudflare</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__tags">
            <span class="tag">Cloudflare</span>
            <span class="tag">systemd</span>
            <span class="tag">HTTPS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card homelab-animate">
        <div class="service-card__status-bar"></div>
        <div class="service-card__content">
          <div class="service-card__header">
            <span class="service-card__dot service-card__dot--live"></span>
            <img class="service-card__icon-img" src="/icons/docker.svg" alt="" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="service-card__name">docker.service</span>
            <span class="service-card__title">- Container Runtime</span>
            <span class="live-pill"><span class="live-pill__dot"></span>LIVE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__meta">
            <span class="service-card__active">Active: active (running)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__details">
            <div class="service-card__row">
              <span class="service-card__key">Version</span>
              <span class="service-card__val">Docker CE + Compose V2 (plugin)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__decisions">
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> Official Docker repo, not Ubuntu's older version</div>
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> systemd-resolved disabled on port 53 for AdGuard</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__tags">
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tag">Compose V2</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card homelab-animate">
        <div class="service-card__status-bar"></div>
        <div class="service-card__content">
          <div class="service-card__header">
            <span class="service-card__dot service-card__dot--live"></span>
            <img class="service-card__icon-img" src="/icons/portainer.svg" alt="" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="service-card__name">portainer.service</span>
            <span class="service-card__title">- Docker Management UI</span>
            <span class="live-pill"><span class="live-pill__dot"></span>LIVE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__meta">
            <span class="service-card__active">Active: active (running)</span>
            <span class="service-card__port">Port: 9000 <span class="port-arrow">-></span> <a href="https://portainer.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">portainer.princejain.me</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__decisions">
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> Full Docker socket access for container management</div>
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> Protected behind Cloudflare Access authentication</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__tags">
            <span class="tag">Portainer</span>
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Data & Privacy -->
    <div class="service-group">
      <div class="service-group__label"><span class="comment-hash">#</span> ─── Data & Privacy ────────────────────────────────</div>

      <div class="service-card homelab-animate">
        <div class="service-card__status-bar"></div>
        <div class="service-card__content">
          <div class="service-card__header">
            <span class="service-card__dot service-card__dot--live"></span>
            <img class="service-card__icon-img" src="/icons/immich.png" alt="" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="service-card__name">immich.service</span>
            <span class="service-card__title">- Self-hosted Photos</span>
            <span class="live-pill"><span class="live-pill__dot"></span>LIVE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__meta">
            <span class="service-card__active">Active: active (running)</span>
            <span class="service-card__port">Port: 2283 <span class="port-arrow">-></span> <a href="https://immich.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">immich.princejain.me</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__details">
            <div class="service-card__row">
              <span class="service-card__key">Stack</span>
              <span class="service-card__val">Server + PostgreSQL (pgvector) + Redis + ML</span>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card__row">
              <span class="service-card__key">Storage</span>
              <span class="service-card__val">Samsung T7 Shield SSD @ /mnt/immich</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__decisions">
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> External SSD for data portability - host can be replaced</div>
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> ML offloaded to GPU node over LAN for face/object detection</div>
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> SSD auto-mounts via UUID in /etc/fstab before Docker starts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__tags">
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="tag">Redis</span>
            <span class="tag">ML</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card homelab-animate">
        <div class="service-card__status-bar"></div>
        <div class="service-card__content">
          <div class="service-card__header">
            <span class="service-card__dot service-card__dot--live"></span>
            <img class="service-card__icon-img" src="/icons/vaultwarden.png" alt="" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="service-card__name">vaultwarden.service</span>
            <span class="service-card__title">- Password Manager</span>
            <span class="live-pill"><span class="live-pill__dot"></span>LIVE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__meta">
            <span class="service-card__active">Active: active (running)</span>
            <span class="service-card__port">Port: 8888 <span class="port-arrow">-></span> <a href="https://vault.princejain.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vault.princejain.me</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__decisions">
            <div class="service-card__decision"><span class="decision-arrow">&gt;</span> Self-hosted Bitwarden - all credentials stay on my hardware</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card__tags">
            <span class="tag">Vaultwarden</span>
            <span class="tag">Bitwarden</span>
          </div>
        </div>
